### FILE: schemas/protobuf/message.proto
```protobuf
syntax = "proto3";

package serialplab;

option java_package = "com.serialplab.proto";
option go_package = "serialplab/proto";

message User {
  string id = 1;
  string name = 2;
  string email = 3;
  int64 timestamp = 4;
}
```

